data.description: Come see this beautiful 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home on a premium oversized lot! This spacious floorplan boasts high ceilings and soft natural light throughout the home from the sprawling windows in the family room. Family room offers wood-type flooring and an inviting gas fireplace. Chef's kitchen features granite countertops, ample cabinetry, and a walkthru to the dining room. Primary bedroom is sure to impress with new carpet, tray ceilings, and ensuite bath offering dual sinks, shower with glass surround, and a deep soaking tub. Texas-sized game room upstairs with 2 more beds up. Make your backyard dreams come true with this pool-sized backyard! Great location to schools, shopping, and dining.
